<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>isInteger() returns true when the given string is a float.</p>

<p>Reproduce code</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
if (Zend_Locale_Format::isInteger('13.445,1', array('locale' =&gt; new Zend_Locale('de_DE')))) {
    print "integer";
} else {
    print "not a integer";
} 
echo "<br />\n";

if (Zend_Locale_Format::isInteger('13,445.1', array('locale' =&gt; new Zend_Locale('en_US')))) {
    print "integer";
} else {
    print "not a integer";
} 

echo "<br />\n";
if (Zend_Locale_Format::isInteger('13445.1', array('locale' =&gt; new Zend_Locale('en_US')))) {
    print "integer";
} else {
    print "not a integer";
} 

echo "<br />\n";
if (Zend_Locale_Format::isInteger('13445,1', array('locale' =&gt; new Zend_Locale('en_US')))) {
    print "integer";
} else {
    print "not a integer";
} 

</code></pre>

<p>All of the strings are detected as integers.</p>

